      <title>当特朗普关税贸易“精疲力尽”时，黄金的价格中断降低了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/gold-s-price-disruption-eases-as-trump-tariff-trade-exhausted</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金的极端价格错位正在逐渐消失，随着物理市场的紧密程度，急于将金条运送到美国的过程可能已经运行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/gold-s-price-disruption-eases-as-trump-tariff-trade-exhausted</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 17:29:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BlockStream为比特币贷款资金确保数十亿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/blockstream-is-said-to-secure-billions-for-bitcoin-lending-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，比特币开发商BlockStream Corp.已获得了数十亿美元的投资，以启动三项资金，其中包括两家将启用加密贷款的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/blockstream-is-said-to-secure-billions-for-bitcoin-lending-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 17:16:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑石的灰色告诉投资者让“关税外交”发挥作用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-04/blackstone-s-gray-tells-investors-to-let-tariff-diplomacy-play-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黑石公司总裁兼首席运营官乔纳森·格雷（Jonathan Gray）表示，投资者应该让“关税外交”发挥作用。他还说，在市场上进行交易和IPO有一种“压抑”的愿望。他在彭博在纽约投资上发表讲话。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-04/blackstone-s-gray-tells-investors-to-let-tariff-diplomacy-play-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 17:14:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密“ ALT季节”可能会在全市范围内消失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/crypto-alt-season-may-disappear-for-good-amid-marketwide-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）连任的旺盛中，加密货币中最可靠的交易模式之一似乎变得不那么可靠。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/crypto-alt-season-may-disappear-for-good-amid-marketwide-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 17:12:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索罗斯（Soros）的菲茨帕特里克（Fitzpatrick）看到信心“从悬崖上掉下来”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-04/soros-fitzpatrick-sees-confidence-falling-off-a-cliff-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[索罗斯基金会（Soros Fund Management）CIO Dawn Fitzpatrick说，消费者的信心和公司信心“正是现在正在悬崖上掉下来的东西，”她讨论了特朗普政府施加的关税的影响。菲茨帕特里克（Fitzpatrick）周二在纽约的彭博投资会议上与埃里克·沙茨克（Erik Schatzker）进行了交谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-04/soros-fitzpatrick-sees-confidence-falling-off-a-cliff-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 17:08:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
