      <title>洛杉矶预计大火后的收入不足1.4亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/la-budget-gaps-grows-after-fires-with-revenue-140-million-short</link>
      <description><![CDATA[洛杉矶估计收入比预算低约1.4亿美元，加深了该市第二连续的年度短缺。]]></description>
