    <item>
      <title>美国给雪佛龙30天在委内瑞拉关闭，挤压马杜罗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/us-treasury-revokes-chevron-license-to-sell-venezuelan-crude</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府正在为雪佛龙公司提供一个月的时间，以停止在委内瑞拉生产石油，对尼古拉斯·马杜罗（Nicolas Maduro）的独裁政权造成了沉重打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/us-treasury-revokes-chevron-license-to-sell-venezuelan-crude</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 15:20:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥比索在关税战争中沉没，在新兴的同龄人中取得收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/tariffs-hit-mexican-peso-as-us-risks-shield-other-em-currencies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对该国征收进口关税之后，墨西哥比索暴跌了，尽管其他发展中国家的货币坚持猜测，随着猜测，贸易战的升级将损害世界上最大的经济体的增长，从而使利益率更高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/tariffs-hit-mexican-peso-as-us-risks-shield-other-em-currencies</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 11:14:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易燃料燃料的“特朗普说”演讲：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心贸易战对全球经济的影响的担忧，股票刺激了股票，这激发了飞往短期债券，黄金和避风港货币的航班。石油倒塌了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 22:46:03 GMT</pubDate>
